summary: This is a brief email chain from December 10, 2018, discussing whether someone had mentioned the Epstein matter to the Office of the Deputy Attorney General (ODAG). The sender notes that a third party had sent a write-up and was awaiting a response.
keyFacts: An email exchange on December 10, 2018, concerns communication about the Epstein case.
The correspondence involves checking whether the matter was mentioned to the Office of the Deputy Attorney General (ODAG).
A third party had reportedly sent a brief write-up on the issue and was awaiting a response at that time.
